data.description: Come Experience this Bridge Bay 55+ boutique community. This lovely residence showcases the spacious Del Webb Mainstay/Summerwood floor-plan, a carefully crafted design boasting three bedrooms, a flex room , three bathrooms, and a large Bonus Room. This home has many luxury upgrades, including Chefs kitchen, extended kitchen island with ample counter space and extra cabinets, walk-in pantry, Kitchen Aid SS appliances, and a 5 burner gas cooktop. Main level has LVP flooring throughout and the flex room has 8' Double doors for privacy. Step through 3 sliding doors onto the screened-in lanai, and the extended paver patio is a perfect way to enjoy the private preserve. Let your imagination run with this 2nd floor oversized bonus room, separate bedroom and bath, an entertainers delight! Enjoy your morning coffee on the upgraded oversized front porch and professionally landscaped front yard. The 3 car tandem garage has lifetime warranty epoxy flooring, electric mosquito screen and a work bench. Water Softener System. This community is maintenance free living. The seller is a Veteran and they have a VA Assumable Loan at 2.25% if a veteran is interested in these details. Enjoy this gated community with its own private heated pool or stay active at the fitness center, play pickleball or tennis and socialization at the clubhouse and explore the community activities. Easy access to I-95,  20 minutes to Vilano Beach and Downtown St. Augustine. Short drive to Costco, Buc ee's, Publix, restaurants and a new Bass Pro & Home Depot coming soon!! Move-In Ready!!
